      • calculateCoverage

        public static double calculateCoverage(NetworkRoute route1,
                                       NetworkRoute route2,
                                       Network network)
        How much of route is "covered" by the links of route2. Based on Ramming. Note that this is not symmetric, i.e. route1 can be fully covered by route2, but not the other way around. kai, nov'13
        Parameters:
        route1 -
        route2 -
        Returns:
        a number between 0 (no coverage) and 1 (route2 fully covers route1)
